arts.ttl: Ajax ease to win over Fortuna Sittard
arts.sum: Ajax eased to a 5-0 win over 10-man Fortuna Sittard on Wednesday evening. Ajax were without the injured Brian Brobbey, while new signings Wout Weghorst and Davy Klaassen were only on the bench. The hosts hadn’t played in a month due to police strikes and they looked fresh from the start.
